{"title":"祝福","authors":["商泽军"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":6,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"祝福"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"商泽军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为非典肆虐下的民众祝福"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为身着隔离服的白衣天使"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那些远离家的父母子女"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祝福"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为那些在城里慌慌张张的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打工的农民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为那些"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不幸感染病毒的人们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祝福"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为那些死去的魂灵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使他们早早地安息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为他们撒上花瓣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为他们的魂灵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祝福"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为那些"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只为一个孩子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开园的幼儿园祝福"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为那些"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈去了前线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而代替妈妈的幼儿园"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祝福"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为那些夫妻同在医院"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"值班"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十几个日日夜夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有归家的家庭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祝福"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为那些蓝天下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞翔的客机"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那些优美的云朵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祝福"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为满载生命希望的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔驰的车轮祝福"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为那些放弃自己的婚礼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写下请战书的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"医生护士"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祝福"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为那些以土地为命的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来自泥土皈依泥土的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农民祝福"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为那些闪着蓝光的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"救护车和"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巡逻车的红绿灯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那些时刻绷着神经的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公安战士祝福"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为那些"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从祖国四面八方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向京城运送的粮食、蔬菜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为那些绿色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祝福"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为那些